Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纠正人类 夺回母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.87,0:00:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的使命...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神会在这次战争中利用你的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.18,0:00:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果战斗了 你的孩子也会死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 不许欺负贞德
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.39,0:00:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一点也没变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.81,0:00:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 你到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.60,0:00:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还愿再陪我跳舞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮大忙了 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.63,0:00:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没想到圣女大人跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.63,0:00:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不是圣女了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.01,0:00:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽塔总在我陷入危机时赶到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.22,0:01:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.61,0:02:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去 我们与人类的关系很好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前 巴哈姆特引发灾难时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们同心协力 付出了巨大牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.79,0:02:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终保住了这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而人类失去了信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宣称不再需要神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后袭击了我们的神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:03:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至犯下了弑神之举
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他们意识到自身的过错之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道我们只能默默忍受此等暴行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不是决不能继续容忍人类的暴行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让侮辱诸神的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.23,0:03:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好见识下我们的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为遇害的同胞雪耻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夺回世界的秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加百列大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔的力量还是未知数
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知能否承受这场战争
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.69,0:04:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔能封印人类的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这己经证明过很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:06.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有退路了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空艇队 上 上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步兵准备好投石车
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把兵力集中到正面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧布置巨神兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:46.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏利欧斯去死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,王宫兵全去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真要打仗就去外面打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死了 再不逃就要开打了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战争将考验我们的真正价值啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与神战斗 你就没任何感想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？那又如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:21.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了 别跟凯撒团长说一样的话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宣战的可是神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.65,0:05:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 辛苦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后勤有劳你们咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:34.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们才是前线的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:35.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吓？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类就在安全地方看戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.58,0:05:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你们的王决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那...那态度是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狄亚思 去干掉他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.56,0:06:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:22.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开火开火开火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这拖着她们 你们先走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.61,0:06:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跑得很快的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.41,0:06:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:06:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再继续走 妮娜就找不到我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什...什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽塔 贞德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来得是时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你俩没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西继续跑下去能到哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没来过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你瞎跳啥舞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那啥...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.61,0:08:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还愿再陪我跳舞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 刹车
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 都抓稳了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:42.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我倒是没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为要挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们在那干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:10.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛啊 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那帮人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥在给我鼓劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.20,0:10:26.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:12:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护好陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂...神是不是太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个光芒能封印人类的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漆黑兵部队在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对付这种对手不是他们的拿手好戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.47,0:14:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连他们也受不了那光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:01.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就跑了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.46,0:15:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报告 城门被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就要杀入城中了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我直言 陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个还未完成开发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在使用 不知陛下会出什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没征求你的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喊你拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:15:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.84,0:16:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我们也差不多该动身了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.05,0:16:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.22,0:16:21.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯撒 把假手摘下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.47,0:16:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摘下来之后固定在锁上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先是伸出拇指 然后是中指
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.74,0:16:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底想干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还用问？当然是要逃出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着弯曲拇指 伸出食指和小拇指
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 尽可能离它远一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:16:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.93,0:17:06.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（咒语）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是什么表情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:21.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会给你做个更好的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能用倒在那里的家伙的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这边的门也打开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你別把我另一只假手也炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个不是我 是丽塔设置的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.59,0:17:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还说什么担心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是都爆炸了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.29,0:18:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.15,0:19:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯撒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.70,0:19:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么在这 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微变得女人些了吗 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.08,0:19:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贞德大人 平安无事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.75,0:19:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯撒 你也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:49.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个 别磨蹭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.98,0:19:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这...这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:19:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.90,0:22:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,【】
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.54,0:23:48.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 你有锻炼自己的本事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.21,0:23:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是锻炼得杠杠的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.26,0:23:52.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招 看招看招
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.51,0:23:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 神击的巴哈姆特 Virgin Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.18,0:23:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告別武装
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.56,0:23:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射击之类的...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.89,0:24:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我不好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.02,0:24:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师傅 别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.98,0:24:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴哈巴哈巴哈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.77,0:24:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周记得看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.02,0:24:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴哈巴哈巴哈魂？